This repository is a ROS 2 Humble and Ubuntu 22.04 port of:

  SCAN-Planner
  https://github.com/wuyi2121/SCAN-Planner

Original research authors:
  Han Zheng, Zhe Chen, Yiwen Fu, Ming Yang, and Tong Qin

Original project:
  SCAN-Planner: Spatial Collision-Aware Local Planning for
  Route-Guided Long-Range Quadruped Navigation
  https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.19555

The upstream project is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
This derivative preserves that license and adds ROS 2 Humble, Ubuntu 22.04,
ament_cmake, colcon, rclcpp, RViz2, tf2_ros and ROS 2 launch integration.

The upstream authors and maintainers are not affiliated with, and do not
necessarily endorse, this port.
